{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b2c-account-gomecano",
    "name": "Gomecano B2C Account API",
    "description": "Collection complète pour tester les fonctions B2C Account\n\n## Configuration requise\n\n1. Définir les variables d'environnement :\n   - `SUPABASE_URL`: URL de votre projet Supabase\n   - `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`: Clé anon publique\n   - `AUTH_TOKEN`: Token JWT après login\n\n2. Pour obtenir un AUTH_TOKEN, utiliser d'abord les requêtes du dossier Auth.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "SUPABASE_URL",
      "value": "https://your-project.supabase.co",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "SUPABASE_ANON_KEY",
      "value": "your-anon-key",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "AUTH_TOKEN",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Authentification Supabase",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "apikey", "value": "{{SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{SUPABASE_URL}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password",
              "host": ["{{SUPABASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "token"],
              "query": [{ "key": "grant_type", "value": "password" }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Current User",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "apikey", "value": "{{SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}}" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{SUPABASE_URL}}/auth/v1/user",
              "host": ["{{SUPABASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "user"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
